\CommentTok{\# \# Define a function to perform paired t{-}test between pairs of columns}
\NormalTok{paired\_t\_test }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \ControlFlowTok{function}\NormalTok{(before, after) \{}
  \FunctionTok{t.test}\NormalTok{(before, after, }\AttributeTok{paired =} \ConstantTok{TRUE}\NormalTok{)}
\NormalTok{\}}

\CommentTok{\# \# Apply paired t{-}test to each pair of pre and post columns}
\NormalTok{results\_EDU }\OtherTok{\textless{}{-}} \FunctionTok{map2}\NormalTok{(edu\_hcomb[}\FunctionTok{grepl}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"PRE"}\NormalTok{, }\FunctionTok{names}\NormalTok{(edu\_hcomb))],}
\NormalTok{                edu\_hcomb[}\FunctionTok{grepl}\NormalTok{(}\StringTok{"POST"}\NormalTok{, }\FunctionTok{names}\NormalTok{(edu\_hcomb))],}
\NormalTok{                paired\_t\_test)}

\CommentTok{\# \# Print the results}
\FunctionTok{print}\NormalTok{(results\_EDU)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}

\CommentTok{\# \# Define a function to perform paired t{-}test between pairs of columns}

\CommentTok{\# \# Apply paired t{-}test to each pair of pre and post columns}

\FunctionTok{print}\NormalTok{(results\_hn)}
\end{Highlighting}
\end{Shaded}
